    "content": "UoB Landscape Statistics Annual Growth Trends Detailed Statistics Track the growth and development of our campus landscape through comprehensive data and visual insights spanning multiple years of environmental enhancement. Visualizing the expansion of our campus landscape initiatives over the years Comprehensive breakdown of landscape development data Total Plant Species Square Meters Completed Projects Campus Locations"
